				}
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Mining"
			x: -4.5d
			y: -2.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["PR01000000000001"]
			description: ["Farming and harvesting produce grants Farming experience. Tier 0 (level 1-20): Wheat, Beetroot, Carrot, Potato. Tier 1 (21-40): Melon, Pumpkin, Tomato, Onion, Cocoa Beans, Rice. Tier 2 (41-60): Corn, Nether Wart, Gysahl Green. Tier 3 (61-80): Pine Fruit, Winter Leaves. Tier 4 (81-100): Scalefruit, Fiery Beans. Tier 5 (100): Cryoroot, Solnut. In-range harvesting drops Tiered Produce — used in Cooking and Alchemy station recipes. A Botany Pot setup growing multiple Pam's HC crops simultaneously is the most efficient way to level Farming."]
			id: "PR01000000000003"
			rewards: [{
				count: 10
