			title: "Farming"
			x: -1.5d
			y: -2.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["PR01000000000001"]
			description: ["Fishing any fish grants Fishing experience. While fishing, there is a chance to catch Tiered Fish — Spiritual (level 1-20), Celestial (21-40), Empyrean (41-60), Angelic (61-80), Divine (81-100), and Godly (100). Tiered Fish are used in Cooking station recipes for seafood dishes that provide Experience and Loot bonus effects. Fishing profession levels feed into the Cooking profession — high-level fish recipes require high-tier fish that only drop at high Fishing levels."]
			id: "PR01000000000004"
			rewards: [{
				count: 10
				id: "PR03000000000004"
				item: "mmorpg:material/fishing/0"
