		}
		{
			dependencies: ["PR01000000000009"]
			description: ["Core Buff Potions target the three primary Mine and Slash stats: Strength, Intelligence, and Dexterity. These are brewed from Tiered Produce, a Common Stone, and secondary vegetables. Strength potions scale Physical Damage and maximum HP; Intelligence scales Spell Damage and Mana; Dexterity scales Attack Speed and Dodge. A set of all three before a difficult atlas map run effectively boosts your build's ceiling for the duration — stack them with food buffs for the highest effective stat totals."]
