		{
			dependencies: ["PR01000000000010"]
			description: ["An Uncommon Armor Infusion requires 3 Spiritual Ore, 1 Uncommon Stone, 2 Iron Ingots, 1 Leather, 1 Paper, and coin. When applied to armor with a successful Common Infusion already applied, it has a chance of adding a stat bonus at Uncommon rarity — a stronger version than what Common infusions can provide. Infusions must be applied in order: Common first, then Uncommon, then Rare, then Epic. The stat bonus from a successful infusion appears in the gear tooltip as a colored Infusion line."]
