				"PR01000000000011"
				"PR01000000000012"
				"PR01000000000013"
				"PR01000000000014"
			]
			description: ["Professions in Mine and Slash are a parallel economy that runs underneath the combat system. Every crafted gear soul, every infusion scroll, every buff potion, and every recovery flask is a product of a profession system that requires dedicated leveling and grinding. A character who ignores professions relies entirely on drops; a character who invests in them shapes their own power curve. The disciplines covered here form the full crafting loop — from salvaging spent gear to crafting better replacements."]
